et loose without worrying about cleanup or potential harm, allowing you to focus solely on the liberating sensation of release.\n\nWhether you're dealing with the pressures of a demanding job, the strains of daily life, or simply seeking an adrenaline-pumping adventure, our VR Rage Room is the ultimate solution. It offers a controlled, yet exhilarating outlet for pent-up energy and frustrations. You'll find yourself fully immersed in an environment designed to facilitate the therapeutic act of venting, leaving you refreshed, rejuvenated, and ready to face the world anew.", "short_description": "Experience a virtual Rage Room: don a headset, grab tools, and let off steam in a mess-free environment. Smash and shatter stress away!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.freeprivacypolicy.com/live/61b6455b-0d88-4260-993d-4766d5c0c188", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Render Island", "support_website_url": "https://www.render-island.com/contact-us", "website_url": "https://www.render-island.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2837265163266059", "context_category": "ENTERTAINMENT"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "842287169851443"}, {"id": "541611600222565"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8204991052941628"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "187947334285452"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "187947334285452"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_t